   <body>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC4947bcc82b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4"></a>Removal of the fuel filler plug
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4446"> </a>Remove the seat (<a href="77991.html#DUC7dd8e1d82a971005810ccc3160c450d2">Removing the seat</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4451"> </a>Remove the front half-fairings (<a href="77983.html#DUC6b420cf82a8210058217e66c96b901d2">Removing the front half-fairing</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4456"> </a>Remove the tank fairings (<a href="77987.html#DUC104f7d582a9610058109cc3160c450d2">Removing the tank fairings</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4462"> </a>Loosen and remove the six screws securing the fuel tank filler cap (1).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4464"> </a>Remove the complete plug (2) having care to recover the two breather hoses (3).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4466"> </a>Recover the sealing washer (4).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4469"> </a>If the filler cap lock needs to be replaced, refer to Section "<a href="77300.html#DUC6b0957e02a6f1005876a8a79606888d2">Removal of the fuel tank filler cap lock</a>" and "<a href="77302.html#DUC991de5d82a6f1005876c8a79606888d2">Installation of the fuel tank filler cap lock</a>".
         </div>
      </div>
